<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:49:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>菲律宾总统称中国海军在南海的存在“令人担忧”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navys-presence-south-china-sea-is-worrisome-says-philippine-president-2024-02-28/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周三表示，中国海军在南海的存在“令人担忧”，但这不会阻止菲律宾保卫其海洋领土和保护其渔民。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:48:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navys-presence-south-china-sea-is-worrisome-says-philippine-president-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国碧桂园因未能偿还2.045亿美元贷款面临清盘申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-faces-winding-up-petition-failure-pay-2045-mln-loan-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国碧桂园控股有限公司周三表示，永信有限公司已向该房地产开发商提交清盘申请，理由是该开发商未偿还价值16亿港元（合2.0449亿美元）的定期贷款。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:47:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-faces-winding-up-petition-failure-pay-2045-mln-loan-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国敦促联合国制定使无核国家免受核威胁的路线图</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-un-define-roadmap-exempt-non-nuclear-states-nuclear-threat-state-2024-02-28/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国外交部军控司表示，联合国裁军谈判会议应制定国际法律文书的路线图或时间表，使无核武器国家免受核武器威胁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-un-define-roadmap-exempt-non-nuclear-states-nuclear-threat-state-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>兄弟姐妹帮助中国比亚迪在泰国电动汽车市场抢占先机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/siblings-help-chinas-byd-grab-early-lead-thai-ev-market-2024-02-27/</link><description>一年多前，比亚迪作为这家中国电动汽车制造商在泰国的唯一全国经销商推出后，Pratarnwong 和 Pratarnporn Phornprapha 兄弟姐妹被迫频繁撕毁商业计划，因为销量不断飙升。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 23:05:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/siblings-help-chinas-byd-grab-early-lead-thai-ev-market-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>应用材料公司收到美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 关于向中国发货的传票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/applied-materials-receives-subpoena-sec-china-shipments-2024-02-27/</link><description>半导体设备供应商应用材料公司在周二提交的文件中表示，该公司二月份收到美国证券交易委员会（SEC）发出的传票，要求提供与某些中国客户发货相关的信息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 22:21:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/applied-materials-receives-subpoena-sec-china-shipments-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：全球货币焦点转向新西兰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-27/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 21:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议员质疑拜登的也门战略，希望得到国会授权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senior-us-senators-want-congress-authorize-strikes-against-houthis-2024-02-27/</link><description>美国民主党和共和党参议员周二质疑乔·拜登总统应对胡塞武装袭击商业航运的战略，并认为他应该寻求国会授权对也门组织持续采取军事行动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 20:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senior-us-senators-want-congress-authorize-strikes-against-houthis-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>ASM International 上半年营收稳定，GAA 和中国需求提振第四季度订单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asm-international-sees-stable-revenues-first-quarter-2024-02-27/</link><description>半导体设备制造商 ASM International 周二预计 2024 年上半年收入稳定，部分原因是其环栅 (GAA) 芯片制造技术推动 2023 年第四季度订单增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 17:36:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asm-international-sees-stable-revenues-first-quarter-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲电动汽车制造商需要更密切的合作才能赶上中国——雷诺首席执行官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europe-ev-makers-need-closer-collaboration-catch-up-with-china-renault-ceo-2024-02-27/</link><description>雷诺老板卢卡·德梅奥周二表示，欧洲汽车制造商和能源供应商需要加强合作，以在电动汽车（EV）行业规模方面赶上中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 15:27:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europe-ev-makers-need-closer-collaboration-catch-up-with-china-renault-ceo-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国对伊朗实施新制裁，针对指挥官和航运</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-hits-iran-with-new-sanctions-targeting-commanders-shipping-2024-02-27/</link><description>美国周二宣布实施制裁，目标是伊朗和胡塞武装指挥官以及一艘向中国企业运送价值超过 1 亿美元伊朗商品的船只。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 14:35:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-hits-iran-with-new-sanctions-targeting-commanders-shipping-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>英国财长与 Shein 主席就伦敦 IPO 进行会谈 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-finance-minister-held-talks-with-shein-chair-about-london-ipo-source-2024-02-27/</link><description>英国政府消息人士告诉路透社，英国财政部长杰里米·亨特已与 Shein 执行主席唐纳德·唐进行了会谈，这家中国创办的快时尚连锁店渴望在伦敦上市。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:51:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-finance-minister-held-talks-with-shein-chair-about-london-ipo-source-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪展示了可以漂浮的SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-off-suv-that-can-also-float-2024-02-27/</link><description>中国比亚迪周二在日内瓦车展上展示了其阳王U8，这是一款豪华插电式混合动力SUV，能够在发生水事故时漂浮。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-off-suv-that-can-also-float-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲数据中心努力应对人工智能驱动的空间需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/european-data-centres-grapple-with-ai-driven-demand-space-2024-02-27/</link><description>行业参与者表示，随着人工智能需求的蓬勃发展与有限的扩展可能性相冲突，欧洲数据中心的空间短缺问题正在加剧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:13:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/european-data-centres-grapple-with-ai-driven-demand-space-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织部长级会议：阿布扎比会议的关键问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/wto-meeting-abu-dhabi-whats-stake-2024-02-27/</link><description>来自世界各地的部长将于 2 月 26 日至 29 日在阿布扎比召开世界贸易组织 (WTO) 部长级会议，试图为全球商业制定新规则，包括改革争端制度和削减渔业补贴。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 12:07:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/wto-meeting-abu-dhabi-whats-stake-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国称地方政府必须防止房地产市场波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-local-governments-should-prevent-property-market-volatility-ministry-2024-02-27/</link><description>中国住房和城乡建设部周二在其网站上表示，中国地方政府应帮助平衡房地产市场的供需。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:22:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-local-governments-should-prevent-property-market-volatility-ministry-2024-02-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>